</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-39_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-40_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-iLLNPL gTJAOY pf-41_">What Is the Health and Safety Executive?
