</span></p><p class="sc-hGMjVM kxdODp pf-46_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-0db65268-cb7a-4bed-a6a9-cd190c1d4037"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Established by the Health and Safety at Work etc. Act 1974, the HSE absorbed several earlier inspectorates, including the Factory Inspectorate and the Railway Inspectorate (later transferred to the Office of Rail and Road).

